org.openstreetmap.osm.data
Class LoadingDataSet

java.lang.Object
  org.openstreetmap.osm.data.LoadingDataSet
All Implemented Interfaces:
IDataSet, IPlugin
public class LoadingDataSet
extends java.lang.Object
implements IDataSet

This DataSet contains 2 child DataSets. It redirects all queries to the first one and if they cannot be answered there it uses the second one.

Author:
Marcus Wolschon
